main event: Several strange objects were observed maneuvering in the sky over Inyokern, California.
interesting points: Three cream colored objects were spotted climbing rapidly to the northeast,Estimated altitude of objects was approximately 20,000 to 32,000 feet,The objects appeared round or balloon-like with strings hanging down,The sighting was made by a civilian at the Inyokern Naval Air Facility and confirmed by other civilians,No photographs or radar tracking was available for the incident.
witness description: civilians at the Inyokern Naval Air Facility
